org.apache.flex.swf.tags

Class DefineButtonCxformTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.swf.tags.Tag
      • org.apache.flex.swf.tags.DefineButtonCxformTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICharacterReferrer, ITag

    public class DefineButtonCxformTag
extends Tag
implements ICharacterReferrer
    Represents a DefineButtonCxform tag in a SWF file.

    DefineButtonCxform defines the color transform for each shape and text character in a button. This is not used for DefineButton2, which includes its own CXFORM.
